For those who dont know what actually is this, these are the Attributes Of God (Allah), For Ex: The first one is "Al Rehman" in Arabic and Urdu الرَّحْمَنُ
Meaning: The Most or Entirely Merciful
Because Allah, bestows His Mercy (Despite Of Disobedients) upon all the creatures in this universe.
So that's why HE is Al Rehman "The Most Merciful"
